id: pm-wxxv
title: Decouple optional package actions from static SDK contracts
description: Decouple Beads/Todos optional package actions from the always-on static SDK tool action schema while preserving installed package command discovery through runtime extension contracts.
type: Task
status: closed
priority: 1
tags[4]: contracts,packages,pm-cli,sdk
