acceptance_criteria: Static SDK core actions no longer imply optional first-party package commands are always core; installed package commands remain discoverable through runtime contracts; MCP/action availability parity is documented or tested; focused SDK/contracts/package tests pass.
parent: pm-59gj
resolution: Completed optional package action decoupling and public SDK type-import cleanup.
expected_result: Static SDK core actions exclude Beads/Todos optional package actions; installed package commands remain discoverable through runtime extension contracts.
actual_result: "Verified static no-extensions contracts reject beads-import while installed package/runtime contracts expose Beads/Todos actions; focused, coverage, temp-project, release, Sentry, and telemetry gates passed."
